"NAME                                    \n"
"    ls - list directory contents.       \n"
"SYNOPSIS                                \n"
"    ls [-s] [path]                      \n"
"DESCRIPTION                             \n"
"    List information about flies        \n"
"    or segments                         \n"
"OPTIONS                                 \n"
"    -s   - list mem sements.            \n"
"    path - path to directory            \n"
"           defaults '/' (root dir).     \n"
"          Path format is /dir/filename. \n"
"SEE ALSO                                \n"
"    rm                                  \n"
